PRICING: Delivery is free for all orders over 5,000 Kč. Standard shipping costs for orders below this value are not specified.
PROVIDERS & TIMEFRAMES: No shipping providers are listed. The dispatch time (expediční lhůta) varies widely from 1 to 21 days depending on the product's stock status, but a final delivery timeframe is not provided.
NOTABLE FEATURES: The main advertised feature is free delivery on orders over 5,000 Kč. There is no mention of express, weekend, or COD services.
WEBSITE ASSESSMENT: The shipping information available on the homepage is very basic. It lacks crucial details such as shipping carriers, standard costs, and specific delivery times. A customer would likely need to proceed to the checkout process to see the full range of options and costs.
